RWF (FOCUS)

for (i in unique(data_1[,'Code'])){
  for (j in colnames(data_1 %>% 
                     filter(Code == i) %>% 
                     select(-c(Code, Year)))) {
    rwf((data_1 %>% 
           filter(Code == i) %>% 
           select(c(j)) %>% ts()), 
        drift=T,
        lambda=0,
        h=10,
        level=80)
  }
}
